data.description: Are you looking for a great location, plenty of space and a double lot? Look no further. This home shows the pride in ownership. Featuring a wood burning fireplace, newer roof, newer AC, fenced in yard, freshly painted, pool with pristine blue water (non-Clorine or salt), French doors, LPV flooring and so much more. This is perfect for any size family.  Plenty of parking and double lot is left wooded for great privacy. 2.99% assumable loan and qualifies for USDA.
